EmailTemplate.name: SunPower Partner Welcome Email Template
EmailTemplate.subject: SunPower Partner Welcome Email
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hello Partner Name,
Welcome to the SunPower Partner network. We look forward to doing business with you.
To ensure that we deal only with authorized staff from your company, kindly fill out the form attached and send back to us as soon as possible.
To help you get started, here are the Guidelines on Placing Orders:
1. The Partner Support Representative assigned to you can assist you on enquiries regarding price, order details, and delivery status. Name: Phone: 1-800 786769 local 38XXX Email: x@sunpowercorp.com
2. Pallet quantities are as follows until further advised. a. SPR 327 34pcs / pallet b. TEN 235 22pcs/ pallet
3. We will confirm the standard transit days from our warehouses once we have received your designated delivery address/es.
4. Please send all orders to au.orders@sunpowercorp.com and your RSM, Name, email address. We will get back to you confirming the receipt of your purchase order and the committed delivery date based on availability.
5. When placing the PO, please include the following information: a. Purchase Order number b. Delivery Address c. Delivery Date (please note the 7-day lead time for metro and 10-day lead time for regional addresses) d. Special instructions e. Contact person and information at delivery site f. Quantity g. Part number and Description h. GST i. Other fees if applicable (Freight cost, non-pallet quantity, tailgate, etc Please refer to the Terms and Conditions on the SunPower Price List).
Once Orders are received, here are the Guidelines upon Delivery:
1. Ensure that you sign the proof of delivery and indicate the date delivered.
We would appreciate if you could send us an email confirmation of the delivery at au.orders@sunpowercorp.com, copying your Partner Support Representative. This will facilitate invoicing.
2. Report any shipping related issues within 10 calendar days upon receipt.
Payment Remittance 1. Your contact from our finance department is Gayle Cron. She can assist regarding any payment issues or statement queries
2. Upon payment remittance, please send the payment remittance advice to SPAU.accountsreceivable@sunpowercorp.com, copying in your PSR, with the related invoice number to ensure that we apply it the intended order.
Please let us know whom we can send the current Price List to. For more information about order placement and the returns policy, you may refer to the Terms and Conditions found on the Price List.
Let me know if you have any questions.
Thank you,
First Name Last Name Job Title
SunPower Corporation Australia Pty Ltd
1-800 SUNPOWER (1-800-786-769)
www.sunpower.com.au
